data.description: If you are looking for a spacious, beautiful home that is just like new, this is the one for you! Built in 2020 and features 4 beds, 3 baths, PLUS an office and flex/gameroom. You will also appreciate the 4 car garage with the 4 garage space having a garage door on both sides. Floored attic with walk-out door provides additional storage space. This home sits on 1 acre +/-  in the peaceful Ruby Estates with no HOA. The huge windows in the living room give you a beautiful view into the backyard, which has plenty of space for a shop, pool, or both. Primary bedroom is downstairs, with one other bedroom and bath. Two bedrooms and one bath upstairs. Beautiful neutral color throughout. Convenient access to HWY 412, HWY 88, and turnpike. You don't want to let this one get away!
